                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When restarting MDT 0 and MDT 1 one by one after a minor upgrade, a flood of this message was printed by MDT 0:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Aug 22 03:16:28 lola-8 kernel: LustreError: 11932:0:(tgt_handler.c:478:tgt_filter_recovery_request()) @@@ not permitted during recovery  req@
ffff88083632dc00 x1477131648377368/t0(0) o901-&amp;gt;soaked-MDT0000-lwp-MDT0001_UUID@192.168.1.109@o2ib:0/0 lens 248/0 e 0 to 0 dl 1408702578 ref 1
 fl Interpret:/0/ffffffff rc 0/-1
[Repeats rapidly...]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Meanwhile from MDT 1:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Aug 22 03:16:07 lola-9 kernel: LustreError: 11-0: soaked-MDT0000-lwp-MDT0001: Communicating with 192.168.1.108@o2ib, operation fld_read faile
d with -11.
[Repeats rapidly...]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
